---
title: Cheesy Lamb Bunless Burger Bowl with Zesty Roast Veggies & Beetroot Relish
description: Don’t worry this type of burger won’t leave you sticky with a giant mess. We’re eliminating the bun and putting these cheesy lamb patties in a bowl so they sit right alongside the chilli-zested roast veggies. There’s a double whammy of flavours from the herby mayo and beetroot relish that will sink into this bowl and deliver a mess-free and tasty burger in a bowl.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
